<FindBugsFilter xmlns="https://github.com/spotbugs/filter/3.0.0">
  <!--
    Reviewed suppressions (Chapter 16: suppress with a reason, never disable a whole detector).

    This module has NONE, which is the chapter's discipline made by the build. The model's value types are
    immutable records (DimensionRating, RoadmapPolicy) and a sealed result of records (NextStep), the
    roadmap view is stateless, and the assessment itself holds only its policy, two atomic counters, and a
    volatile int — it exposes no array or mutable collection, so the representation-exposure detectors stay
    quiet without any suppression. The filter is kept (empty) so a future, genuinely-reviewed suppression
    has a home with a reason rather than being added inline.
  -->
</FindBugsFilter>
